description: [``botocore``] This release adds tagging support for Amazon Managed Service for Prometheus workspace.

[``botocore``] Predictor creation now supports selecting an accuracy metric to optimize in AutoML and hyperparameter optimization. This release adds additional accuracy metrics for predictors - AverageWeightedQuantileLoss, MAPE and MASE.
[``botocore``] Updated references to AWS KMS keys and customer managed keys to reflect current terminology.
[``botocore``] SPEKE v2 support for live CMAF packaging type. SPEKE v2 is an upgrade to the existing SPEKE API to support multiple encryption keys, it supports live DASH currently.
[``botocore``] Adding RegisterCluster and DeregisterCluster operations, to support connecting external clusters to EKS.
